original: Christiansson, Signe Ingeborg, tandläkare, Göteborg, f. 8/11/04 i Röstånga, Malmöh. 1., av Axel C. o. Elise Cal’1-mer. Stud:ex. v. Eslövs h. samisk. 24, tandl :kand. 26, tandläkare 29. Tandläkare v. Gbgs kommun, tandpolikliniker 29.
translated: Christiansson, Signe Ingeborg, dentist, Gothenburg, born November 8th, 1904 in Röstånga, Malmöhus County. First child of Axel C. and Elise Cal’1-mer. Passed student exam at Eslöv high school in 1924. Completed dental studies in 1926 and became a licensed dentist in 1929. Worked as a dentist for Gothenburg municipality at dental clinics since 1929.
